Islamabad United became the first ever team to win Pakistan Super League in 2016. And Now The Federal Team Is Participating In The Pakistan Cup The Team Is Under Captinacy of Misbah-ul-Haq Former Captain Of Pakistan, The Islambad United Was Also Under Misbah.





